Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.01,0:24:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...drive a certain young star reader\Nto take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.68,0:24:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Shuga Thirsts."
